@model GrcMvc.Models.DTOs.UpdateAuditDto
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Localization
@inject IHtmlLocalizer<SharedResource> L
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = L["Audit_Edit_Title"].Value;
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row mb-3">
        <div class="col">
            <h2><i class="bi bi-pencil-square"></i> @L["Audit_Edit_Title"]</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col text-end">
            <a asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> @L["BackToList"]
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
            <form asp-action="Edit">
                <div asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly" class="text-danger"></div>

                <div class="row mb-3">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Name" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_Name"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="Name" class="form-control" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="Name" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="AuditNumber" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_Number"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="AuditNumber" class="form-control" readonly />
                            <span asp-validation-for="AuditNumber" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Type" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_Type"]</label>
                            <select asp-for="Type" class="form-select">
                                <option value="Internal">@L["Audit_Type_Internal"]</option>
                                <option value="External">@L["Audit_Type_External"]</option>
                                <option value="Compliance">@L["Audit_Type_Compliance"]</option>
                                <option value="Financial">@L["Audit_Type_Financial"]</option>
                                <option value="IT">@L["Audit_Type_IT"]</option>
                                <option value="Operational">@L["Audit_Type_Operational"]</option>
                            </select>
                            <span asp-validation-for="Type" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row mb-3">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="PlannedStartDate" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_PlannedStart"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="PlannedStartDate" class="form-control" type="date" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="PlannedStartDate" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="PlannedEndDate" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_PlannedEnd"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="PlannedEndDate" class="form-control" type="date" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="PlannedEndDate" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="ActualStartDate" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_ActualStart"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="ActualStartDate" class="form-control" type="date" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="ActualStartDate" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="ActualEndDate" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_ActualEnd"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="ActualEndDate" class="form-control" type="date" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="ActualEndDate" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group mb-3">
                    <label asp-for="Description" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Description"]</label>
                    <textarea asp-for="Description" class="form-control" rows="3"></textarea>
                    <span asp-validation-for="Description" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group mb-3">
                    <label asp-for="Scope" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_Scope"]</label>
                    <textarea asp-for="Scope" class="form-control" rows="3"></textarea>
                    <span asp-validation-for="Scope" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>

                <div class="row mb-3">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Objectives" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_Objectives"]</label>
                            <textarea asp-for="Objectives" class="form-control" rows="3"></textarea>
                            <span asp-validation-for="Objectives" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Criteria" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_Criteria"]</label>
                            <textarea asp-for="Criteria" class="form-control" rows="3"></textarea>
                            <span asp-validation-for="Criteria" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group mb-3">
                    <label asp-for="Methodology" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_Methodology"]</label>
                    <textarea asp-for="Methodology" class="form-control" rows="3"></textarea>
                    <span asp-validation-for="Methodology" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>

                <div class="row mb-3">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="LeadAuditor" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_LeadAuditor"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="LeadAuditor" class="form-control" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="LeadAuditor" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="AuditTeam" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_Team"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="AuditTeam" class="form-control" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="AuditTeam" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Status" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_Status"]</label>
                            <select asp-for="Status" class="form-select">
                                <option value="Planned">@L["Audit_Status_Planned"]</option>
                                <option value="Scheduled">@L["Audit_Status_Scheduled"]</option>
                                <option value="InProgress">@L["Audit_Status_InProgress"]</option>
                                <option value="Fieldwork">@L["Audit_Status_Fieldwork"]</option>
                                <option value="Reporting">@L["Audit_Status_Reporting"]</option>
                                <option value="Completed">@L["Audit_Status_Completed"]</option>
                                <option value="Cancelled">@L["Audit_Status_Cancelled"]</option>
                            </select>
                            <span asp-validation-for="Status" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card bg-light mb-3">
                    <div class="card-header fw-bold">@L["Audit_ReportDetails"]</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                         <div class="row mb-3">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <div class="form-group mb-3">
                                    <label asp-for="RiskRating" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_RiskRating"]</label>
                                    <select asp-for="RiskRating" class="form-select">
                                        <option value="">@L["Audit_SelectRating"]</option>
                                        <option value="Critical">@L["Audit_RiskRating_Critical"]</option>
                                        <option value="High">@L["Audit_RiskRating_High"]</option>
                                        <option value="Medium">@L["Audit_RiskRating_Medium"]</option>
                                        <option value="Low">@L["Audit_RiskRating_Low"]</option>
                                        <option value="Effective">@L["Audit_RiskRating_Effective"]</option>
                                    </select>
                                    <span asp-validation-for="RiskRating" class="text-danger"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                         </div>
                         <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="ExecutiveSummary" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_ExecutiveSummary"]</label>
                            <textarea asp-for="ExecutiveSummary" class="form-control" rows="4"></textarea>
                            <span asp-validation-for="ExecutiveSummary" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="KeyFindings" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_KeyFindings"]</label>
                            <textarea asp-for="KeyFindings" class="form-control" rows="4"></textarea>
                            <span asp-validation-for="KeyFindings" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="ManagementResponse" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Audit_ManagementResponse"]</label>
                            <textarea asp-for="ManagementResponse" class="form-control" rows="3"></textarea>
                            <span asp-validation-for="ManagementResponse" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group mt-4">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="bi bi-save"></i> @L["SaveChanges"]
                    </button>
                    <a asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">@L["Cancel"]</a>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    @{await Html.RenderPartialAsync("_ValidationScriptsPartial");}
}
